{"tid":2129593,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"始終都係覺得沙士氣氛沉重過武肺 [香討版本]","createTime":"2020-07-28T16:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T13:14:50.000Z","uid":227275,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58f2cc38f52cf415fd974b14afb2c9785c52e953","tid":2129593,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=29257948&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D29257948%26extra%3Dpage%253D1%26page%3D1&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=6067a690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=29257948&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無聊入去睇下班香討狗會唔會屌柒政府<br />\n點撚知有人抄POST<br />\nD留言仲好笑<br />\n<br />\n武肺梗係唔勁啦！美肺先致有殺傷力吖嘛！<br />\n嗱！你睇吓！超過4百萬美肺染疫大軍喇！你話美肺係唔係最勁先？<img src=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/foshantou/fst_evil.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Ffoshantou%2Ffst_evil.gif&h=3b865fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老母生左你就真係冇肺<img src=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default/titter.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Ftitter.gif&h=3a3d2eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老母系經歷過先好講，當年邊有咁多政治閪系度玩嘢，啱啱想戴口罩個疫情就過咗。<br />\n<br />\n如果你現在身處於美國，保證讓你感受到比沙士更沉重。無皇管、唔撚戴罩、買唔到罩，政府派條毛，你感染就LLL，你撚你！<br />\n<br />\n沒有武肺,<span class=\"xx-large\">只有美肺!!</span><br />\n<br />\n我只知咩叫美肺 乜L野武肺？DLLM！你老母就廢！<br />\n<br />\n當年冇黑醫護，最多咪有個&ldquo;10點前特首&rdquo;，吹吓牛<br />\n記得當時有位中咗沙士醫生康復後，開記招，要打好呢場仗，專心一戰<br />\n唔似依家出咗咁多黑醫護<br />\n動不動要罷工，搞呢樣搞果樣，反政府，揾病人較飛,咁冇醫德<br />\n<br />\n美癈真仆街。令美國放棄冶療攬炒全世界 ，有邊個國家唔係比佢累死。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39f7422c363d8dca0d97faef5e36ef0c40baef8","tid":2129593,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb106be16e8e2b01ed51f542adc79241673d22c2","tid":2129593,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62d4f15dddd871eecf92999a5b997853fe260b0","tid":2129593,"uid":168381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"兒登已經低低地，睇埋鄉土，何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96d15e3d057267a9f0def77bcabbe3925563f3a","tid":2129593,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d62d4f15dddd871eecf92999a5b997853fe260b0","tid":2129593,"uid":168381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"兒登已經低低地，睇埋鄉土，何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:13:44.000Z","msg":"睇下佢地手停口停仲點支持政府啊嘛<br />\n點知又真係乜都up得出"},{"pid":"2ad379c1c494b733be0434bb03edeca0a9cc5b0e","tid":2129593,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de9cb0e4797fa088b0b4f017c15048ed64249b1","tid":2129593,"uid":45673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b96d15e3d057267a9f0def77bcabbe3925563f3a","tid":21